{"tid":1262173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【撐香港】何韻詩、明哥將與台灣音樂人聯手推新歌《撐》　林夕有份填詞","createTime":"2019-06-27T14:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T07:46:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fd5367ea85041df2ddf1b39df05afc01e37c8d","tid":1262173,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:41:14.000Z","msg":"反送中浪潮持續，台灣傳媒報道，香港歌手何韻詩、台灣樂團「滅火器」等近20組音樂人獻唱，聲援香港的反送中運動。《撐》歌曲以國語、粵語歌唱穿插，希望用自由的台灣，《撐》香港的自由。歌曲預計本週推出，聲援香港7月1日的遊行。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《自由時報》今日報道，《撐》歌曲以國語、粵語歌唱穿插，此曲由三金音樂製作人柯智豪統籌製作，並由台灣知名音樂作詞人武雄、香港音樂作詞人林夕共同填詞，董事長樂團主唱吳永吉作曲。<br />\n<br />\n歌曲並集合了台港近20個樂團、歌手獻唱，包含何韻詩、黃耀明、董事長樂團、滅火器樂團、巴奈等音樂人，跨海串連一起「撐香港」。<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩今日接受《蘋果》訪問確認會推出新歌，她表示歌曲由台灣發起，她與黃耀明都是獲邀合，。歌詞與創作歌曲原意都是想表達一種訊息：台灣人會聲援香港抗爭中的人。"},{"pid":"0c52619f8cd3312953801b8466df7a829a942868","tid":1262173,"uid":205339,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又黎"},{"pid":"af002d2071d693116ef6395b26b39f8fc11b2c89","tid":1262173,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"8c11df30e15374d8ae4c8f56f9ce7012deadca4c","tid":1262173,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"4655098af83c9ff3b44a01874885d395df51b15f","tid":1262173,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c11df30e15374d8ae4c8f56f9ce7012deadca4c","tid":1262173,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ssCWcBNqvnc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DssCWcBNqvnc&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=4256310f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ssCWcBNqvnc</a>"},{"pid":"7700caae78a5f38aec19324fe12310f3ee88aafb","tid":1262173,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"聽完都幾感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港藝人簡直就係垃圾 為錢出賣靈魂"}]}